                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Discover the magic of Paris, from the Eiffel Tower to its beautiful museums and art galleries. Paris is the perfect destination for art lovers, food enthusiasts, and those seeking romance!</p>
