        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Китай Модал -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="chinaModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="chinaModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="chinaModalLabel">Great Wall of China</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Walk along the historic Great Wall of China, one of the Seven Wonders of the World. Marvel at the stunning views and explore the rich cultural history of China.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Сидни Модал -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="sydneyModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="sydneyModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="sydneyModalLabel">Sydney - Opera House</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Experience Sydney's famous Opera House and enjoy the stunning views of Sydney Harbour. The city is known for its iconic landmarks and beautiful beaches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Мачу Пикчу Модал -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="machuPicchuModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="machuPicchuModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="machuPicchuModalLabel">Machu Picchu - Inca Civilization</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Explore the ancient Inca city of Machu Picchu in the Andes. A stunning archaeological site that offers breathtaking views and a deep dive into the history of the Inca civilization.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
